YouMarie Humbert bụ onye Switzerland - Ghana na-eme ihe nkiri

Ọ natara nhọpụta abụọ na 2016 Ghana Movie Awards maka nchọpụta kachasị mma na onye na-eme ihe nkiri kachasị mma, yana na 10th Africa Movie Academy Awards maka onye na-akwado ihe nkiri kachasị ike. Ya na ezinụlọ ya tolitere na mba isii
Nna ya bụ onye Swiss French si Geneva na nne ya bụ onye Ghana si Akim Oda, na mpaghara Ọwụwa Anyanwụ.

Humbert mere "Ebaner" na 40 na Single, onye mmeri nke ndị na-ege ntị maka onye na-anya ụgbọelu na 2018 LA Film Festival na "Susan" na Potomanto, nke bụ ihe nkiri mbụ ya ma nweta Africa Movie Academy Award maka onye na'eme ihe nkiri kacha mma na nhọpụta nkwado na nhọpụta Ghana Movie Award. Ọ rụrụ "Makena" na An African City, na-akọwa ọrụ ya na ihe nkiri ahụ dị ka ngosipụta nke ahụmịhe onwe ya nke ịkwaga Ghana afọ ole na ole gara aga

Ọ kọwara Issa Rae na Meryl Streep n'etiti ndị ọzọ dị ka ndị ọkachamara ụlọ ọrụ na-akpali ya. Na 2016 Ghana Movie Awards, Humbert natara nhọpụta maka onye na-eme ihe nkiri kachasị mma na usoro ihe nkiri na nchọpụta nke ụdị afọ
Emume mmeri e mere na Kempinski Gold Coast Hotel, Accra na Disemba. Marie gosipụtara na nso nso a na ihe nkiri Netflix nke 2020 The Set Up
Humbert bụ onye Ghana na Switzerland

Ọ gụrụ ihe nkiri na Cours Florent na Paris ebe ọ natara ihe nrite Lesley Chatterley maka onye na-eme ihe nkiri kacha mma na 2009. Tupu nke ahụ, ọ natara nzere bachelọ nke nka na Mahadum Deakin dị na Melbourne, Australia, na-agụ akwụkwọ n'ihe gbasara ime ihe nkiri
Ọ na-asụ Bekee na French nke ọma.
